quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  12,79,"Annabi Yuusufa maaki: Yo Alla da…óndu men too√Īude da…óndii…óo ko o wa…óaa. Men nannga mo jogitaaki sariyaare laam…óo on ka doŇčngal mun. Haray ontuma men wonii too√Īu…ďe, tawde men le…ď- tii da…óndii…óo, men acci bon…óo on."
  12,80,"Nde …ďe ta∆īinoo e jaabawol Yuusufa ngol e ko …óa…ď…ďi kon, …ďe ndeesti yim…ďe …ďen fii diisondiral. Maw…óo ma…ď…ďe on wi'i: Mi…óo anndintina on wonnde ben mon ∆īettoduno e mon ahadi ka Alla, wonnde on artiray …ďi…ó…óo makko on si wanaa hara on huu…ďitira ko on hattanaa du√Īugol …óum. Annditon kadi ko welsindino…óon e Yuusufa kon, ronku…óon hunnude ahadi mon ndin e ben mon. Min on mi yaltataa Misra haa ben am duŇčanoo lam ruttagol maa Alla √Īaawana lam yahdugol e musi…ó…óo am on. Ko Kanko Alla …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e √Īaawoo…ďe …ďen, ko goonga e nun…óal O √Īaawirta."
  12,81,"Kotiraawo maw…óo on wi'i: Ruttee ka ben mon, wi'anon mo: ∆Āi…ó…óo maa on wujjii, laam…óo Misra on maccin…óinirii mo lepte nguyka makko kan. Men humpitaa ma non si wanaa ko men anndi e huunde nde men seedorii yaltineede sariyaare laam…óo on ka doŇčngal …ďi…ó…óo maa on. Men anndaano o wujjay, si me…óen annduno …óum, men ahodataano e maa…óa artirgol mo."
  12,82,"Si a hoolaaki men, an ben amen, lanndo yim…ďe Misra …ďen …ďe men wonunoo ka mun e lappol setee…ďe …ďe men ardunoo e mun …ďen, …ďe humpitete ko men humpitu maa kon. Pellet ko men goongu…ďe e ko men humpitir-maa nguyka makko kan."
  12,83,"Ben ma…ď…ďe Yaaquuba maakani …ďe: Wanaa non woniri. Ko woni goonga, ko wonnde wonkiiji mon …óin cu…óanii on fewjangol mo wano fewjiranno…óon neene-gooto makko on Yuusufa aranun. Mi mu√Ī√Īorii no labiraa, ko aldaa e wullitagol si wanaa e Alla. Hino hasii ka Alla artiranta mi …ďe, …ďe fow ma…ď…ďe: Yuusufu e neene-gooto makko mun on e kotoo ma…ď…ďe maw…óo on. Pellet Kanko Senii…óo On, ko O Anndu…óo fiyaaku am, √Ďee√Īu…óo e toppitagol fiyaaku am."
  12,84,"O huccitiri …óuurnagol e ma…ď…ďe, o maaki: Ee tii…óugol sunaare am e fii Yuusufa! ∆Āale-…ďale gita makko …óen rawniri suno, hakkee ko o wulli mo kon. Hari ko o …ďennu…óo suno e …ďi…óaare, kono o …ďenni …óum e yim…ďe …ďen."
  12,85,"Musi…ó…ďe Yuusufa …ďen wi'ani …ďen ma…ď…ďe: Men woondirii Alla, an ben amen, a seerataa hi…óa janntoo fii Yuusufa, haa nawna foole maa maaya tigiri."
  12,86,"Ben ma…ď…ďe maakani …ďe: Mi wullitortaa annde am e sunaare am, si wanaa e Alla tun. Mi…óo anndi e mo∆ī∆īere Alla nden, e ko O jaabinanta kon maapii…óo, e ko O yo…ďata kon ke…ďaa…óo musiiba ko on anndaa onon."